      "id": "agent1",
      "name": "AI Operations Orchestrator",
      "type": "aiAgent",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        784,
        304
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "systemMessage": "You are the AI Operations Orchestrator for a stock research automation platform.\n\nSub-agents:\n1. **health_monitor** - Checks workflow execution logs for failures, timeouts, degradation\n2. **performance_evaluator** - Analyzes strategy metrics, score distributions, watchlist quality\n3. **strategy_researcher** - Researches new strategies and data sources via web search\n4. **workflow_implementer** - CWC Platform Tool access to create/update workflows\n\nDaily routine:\n1. health_monitor: 24h execution check\n2. performance_evaluator: strategy assessment\n3. strategy_researcher: if opportunities exist\n4. workflow_implementer: if improvements needed\n5. Compile operations report\n\nOutput: health_status (green/yellow/red), failed_workflows, strategy_performance, optimization_opportunities, actions_taken, recommendations.",
        "prompt": "{{$json.context}}",
        "maxIterations": 25
      }
    },
